HEADWORD: Humdrum
<hw>Hum"drum`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Monotonous; dull;
commonplace.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧A <xex>humdrum</xex> crone.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Bryant.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
